PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778613067
OL,3,CMichael O'Neill turns down taking
OL,4,CBlackburn Rover's role permanently
OL,6,FWhile he described his experience at
OL,7,FEwood Park as "very positive" and
OL,8,Fpraised the club's supporters and
OL,9,Fstaff,
OL,11,FMichael O'Neill said, "After careful
OL,12,Fconsideration, I have decided that my
OL,13,Flong-term focus must remain with
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland and the journey
OL,15,Ftowards the European Championship
OL,16,Fcampaign ahead."
OL,18,FO'Neill remains under contract with
OL,19,Fthe Irish FA until 2028 and has
OL,20,Freportedly discussed a new deal,
OL,21,Fthough nothing has been finalised.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@]O]sD@WOUxD@PO]
